data.description: Welcome to your new home! This charming residence features recent remodeling, adding a touch of modernity to its classic appeal. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this cozy abode provides a comfortable living space for you and your family. The highlight of the property is its spacious backyard, perfect for hosting gatherings and creating wonderful memories. Embrace the warmth and character of this inviting home, where both comfort and style come together seamlessly. Don't miss out!
